{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname ProductID}{\xmlattrvalue La Corte}}}la Corte{\*\xmlclose} preserva la que se ajusta a {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PersonName}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname ProductID}{\xmlattrvalue la Constituci\'f3n}}}
